The agent-seed feature (selectable, per-language/per-domain repository guidance
served over MCP) is inspired by the "agent-seed" pattern — a markdown-first,
layered repo-guidance seed. The guidance text shipped here is original to this
project; the design owes the layered taxonomy and the anti-one-shot framing to
that prior art.

